 \frac{1}{\cos z}= 1+\sum_{n=-\infty}^{\infty}(-1)^{n+1}\Big (\frac{1}{z-\frac{\pi}{2}-\pi n}+\frac{1}{\frac{\pi}{2}+\pi n}\Big) 
\frac{1}{\cos x}  = \sum_{n=0}^{\infty}(-1)^{n+1}\frac{(2n+1)\pi}{z^{2}-(\frac{2n+1}{2})^{2}\pi^2} 
 \frac{1}{\cos z}= 1+\sum_{n=-\infty}^{1}(-1)^{n+1}\Big (\frac{1}{z-\frac{\pi}{2}-\pi n}+\frac{1}{\frac{\pi}{2}+\pi n}\Big) + \sum_{n=0}^{\infty}(-1)^{n+1}\Big (\frac{1}{z-\frac{\pi}{2}-\pi n}+\frac{1}{\frac{\pi}{2}+\pi n}\Big) 
 = 1 + \sum_{n=1}^{\infty}(-1)^{n+1}\Big (\frac{1}{z-\frac{\pi}{2}+\pi n}+\frac{1}{\frac{\pi}{2}-\pi n}\Big) + \sum_{n=0}^{\infty}(-1)^{n+1}\Big (\frac{1}{z-\frac{\pi}{2}-\pi n}+\frac{1}{\frac{\pi}{2}+\pi n}\Big) 
\Big (\frac{1}{z-\frac{\pi}{2}-\pi n}+\frac{1}{\frac{\pi}{2}+\pi n}\Big)
\sum_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac1{z-\frac{\pi}{2}-\pi n}
